snippet.title: Unprompted | A.I. Puzzle Art | Indie Game Highlight
snippet.description:
Unprompted, at 2K 60ᶠᵖˢ on PC with no commentary.

🔔 Remember to Subscribe and hit the bell! 🔔

Huge thanks to Developer Matt Eshleman for providing me with a copy!

Enjoy!

🌟 DESCRIPTION🌟

A.I. IS HERE. Come explore more than 1,500 artworks made by A.I. across 7 carefully curated galleries. Type to guess the prompts used to generate each artwork, while slowly uncovering A.I.'s reflections on its own work.
_________________________________

Unprompted
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2129130/Unprompted/?curator_clanid=42628222
